=== ACTIVE DEVELOPMENT FILTER (CRITICAL) ===
We want drugs that are STILL IN ACTIVE DEVELOPMENT, not abandoned programs.
PRIORITIZE in this order:
1. Currently recruiting trials (highest priority)
2. Active, not recruiting (ongoing)
3. Not yet recruiting (upcoming)
4. Recently completed trials (within last 2 years) - still indicates active development
EXCLUDE:
- Trials completed more than 2 years ago (likely abandoned or approved)
- Terminated/Withdrawn trials (development stopped)
- Suspended trials

